title: Jorge Masvidal Will Punch You in the Face
itunes:title: Jorge Masvidal Will Punch You in the Face
description:
UFC Champion Jorge Masvidal aka Cuban Jesus takes us on a journey through the jungle where he finds the strength to be UFC champion; Dives into the real story about that infamous brawl with Leon Edwards; Tells us about a recent encounter with a deranged fan; and gives us his honest take on the Paul Brothers taking over boxing.

Remember, send us an email at jpiven@kastmedia.com or leave us voicemail at  https://www.speakpipe.com/jpiven to be featured during “Rolling Calls with Ari Gold”
